kitchen scripts:


1. cd into the cookbook directory
2. make up metadata.rb, recipes and environments directories
3. in ./recipes make up cookbook files, in ./environments make up json files
4. below link is a needed file for vagrant

https://opscode-omnibus-packages.s3.amazonaws.com/ubuntu/10.04/x86_64/chef_12.3.0-1_amd64.deb

and it will do something like
downloading https://opscode-omnibus-packages.s3.amazonaws.com/ubuntu/10.04/x86_64/chef_12.3.0-1_amd64.deb
         to file /tmp/install.sh.1197/chef_12.3.0-1_amd64.deb

5. in the cookbook directory, run scripts

kitchen init
kitchen converge
kitchen destroy